OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start for many,
OL,6,Falthough low cloud quickly burning
OL,7,Faway. Sunny spells follow, but also
OL,8,Fsome patchy higher cloud. Despite very
OL,9,Fwarm sunshine, it will feel a little
OL,10,Fcooler in the north and northeast due
OL,11,Fto the onshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FWinds easing to become mainly
OL,14,Flight inland, but staying breezing
OL,15,Falong the coast. Low cloud is also
OL,16,Flikely to spill inland, however some
OL,17,Fclearer spells remain likely across
OL,18,Fwestern parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
