OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSimilar to Thursday, with any
OL,6,Fcloud clearing through the morning, to
OL,7,Fgive good sunny spells. However
OL,8,Ffeeling a touch cooler, with a light
OL,9,Fnortherly breeze, fresher into north
OL,10,FNorfolk coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,13,Fand dry, with plenty of sunny spells
OL,14,Fand likely staying clearer overnight.
OL,15,FCooler than recent days with
OL,16,Ftemperatures easing to nearer normal
OL,17,Ffor mid-July.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
